    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You learn to inspire your allies into motion, gaining the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase your Charisma score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>As a bonus action, you can expend one use of your Bardic Inspiration to choose a number of creatures you can see and that can see you within 60 feet of you, up to a number equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1). Each creature you choose can immediately use its reaction to move up to its speed, without provoking opportunity attacks.</li>\n</ul>",
